description.detailed_html:
Patch for a Thrift union.

The Patch template parameter must be a Thrift struct with the following fields:

  • optional T assign

  • terse bool clear

  • terse P patchPrior

  • terse T ensure

  • terse P patch Where P is the field patch type for the union type T.
